headline: Reflecting On Regional Banks Stocks’ Q2 Earnings: Citizens Financial Group (NYSE:CFG)
summary: The end of the earnings season is always a good time to take a step back and see who shined (and who not so much). Let’s take a look at how regional banks stocks fared in Q2, starting with Citizens Financial Group (NYSE:CFG).
